### File 3 — `.dockerignore`
```
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.egg-info/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Secrets — NEVER bake these into the image
.env
*.env

# SQLite databases — these live on the host via volumes
*.db

# Git
.git/
.gitignore

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# Logs
*.log
```

